jasperReport.name: rp-refer
jasperReport.queryString:
SELECT b_site.site_full_name AS site_name ,r_referout.description AS referout ,case when (sum(q1.c_comm) > 0 ) then (sum(q1.c_comm)) else 0 end AS c_comm ,case when (sum(q1.w_warr) > 0 ) then (sum(q1.w_warr)) else 0 end AS w_warr ,case when (sum(q1.s_std) > 0 ) then (sum(q1.s_std)) else 0 end AS s_std ,case when (sum(q1.s_sold) > 0 ) then (sum(q1.s_sold)) else 0 end AS s_sold ,case when (sum(q1.e_employ) > 0 ) then (sum(q1.e_employ)) else 0 end AS e_employ ,case when (sum(q1.f_fam) > 0 ) then (sum(q1.f_fam)) else 0 end AS f_fam ,case when (sum(q1.c_civil) > 0 ) then (sum(q1.c_civil)) else 0 end AS c_civil ,sum(q1.c_comm+q1.w_warr+q1.s_std+q1.s_sold+q1.e_employ+q1.f_fam+q1.c_civil) AS total
FROM b_site,r_referout
LEFT JOIN (select f_visit_refer_type.f_visit_refer_type_id as f_visit_refer_type_id ,(CASE WHEN ((t_health_family.f_person_rank_id ='1') AND ( t_patient.f_sex_id='1'OR t_patient.f_sex_id='2')) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS c_comm
,(CASE WHEN ((t_health_family.f_person_rank_id ='2') AND ( t_patient.f_sex_id='1'OR t_patient.f_sex_id='2')) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS w_warr
,(CASE WHEN ((t_health_family.f_person_rank_id ='3') AND ( t_patient.f_sex_id='1'OR t_patient.f_sex_id='2')) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS s_std
,(CASE WHEN ((t_health_family.f_person_rank_id ='4') AND ( t_patient.f_sex_id='1'OR t_patient.f_sex_id='2')) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS s_sold ,(CASE WHEN ((t_health_family.f_person_rank_id ='5') AND ( t_patient.f_sex_id='1'OR t_patient.f_sex_id='2')) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS e_employ
,(CASE WHEN ((t_health_family.f_person_rank_id ='6') AND (t_patient.f_sex_id='1'OR t_patient.f_sex_id='2')) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS f_fam
,(CASE WHEN ((t_health_family.f_person_rank_id ='7') AND ( t_patient.f_sex_id='1'OR t_patient.f_sex_id='2')) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS c_civil
FROM t_patient INNER JOIN t_visit ON t_patient.t_patient_id = t_visit.t_patient_id INNER JOIN t_visit_refer_in_out ON t_visit.t_visit_id = t_visit_refer_in_out.t_visit_id INNER JOIN f_visit_refer_type ON t_visit_refer_in_out.f_visit_refer_type_id = f_visit_refer_type.f_visit_refer_type_id inner join t_health_family on t_patient.t_health_family_id = t_health_family.t_health_family_id where t_visit.f_visit_status_id <> '4' AND substring(t_visit.visit_financial_discharge_time,1,10) Between $P{start_date} AND $P{end_date}
) q1
ON r_referout.refer_type_id = q1.f_visit_refer_type_id
group by b_site.site_full_name ,r_referout.description ,q1.f_visit_refer_type_id
order by q1.f_visit_refer_type_id ASC
